<h1>Alcohol Withdrawal Nursing Guide 2026: CIWA &amp; DTs Management</h1>
<p class="hub-crumb" style="font-family:sans-serif;font-size:0.9em;background:#f0f4ff;border-left:4px solid #3b6cf8;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;margin:14px 0;">Part of the <a href="icu-emergencies-hub-2026.html"><strong>ICU Emergencies Hub</strong></a> &mdash; browse every related guide in one place.</p>
<div class="danger"><strong>Alcohol withdrawal can be fatal.</strong> Unlike opioid withdrawal (uncomfortable but rarely deadly), severe alcohol withdrawal (delirium tremens) carries 5&ndash;15% mortality without treatment. Benzodiazepines save lives.</div>
